fips:USCounty5DigitCodeSimpleType

simpleType USCounty5DigitCodeSimpleType in namespace http://release.niem.gov/niem/codes/fips/5.0/

Definition

A data type for unique 5-digit US county codes, with a 2-digit state code followed by a 3-digit county code.
